ygData.messageBody:
/rofl

I was thinking the same thing last nite! Of course I was one of the few
deaths anyhow. To think I might actually gain a level in one week is mind
boggling to me. Of course, having 3 bards to spread that gobbie luv around
so to speak certainly helped. Two nights before I was the sole bard and
died three times because no one could get the mobs off me. If not for the
bizarre chain-trolling as we called it where I was the bait while the other
bard chained/whacked I would have died again.

Kitasi
